# 🌊 Flood Prediction System using Machine Learning

## 📌 Project Description

The Flood Prediction System is an AI and Machine Learning-based web application that predicts flood risk using historical disaster and environmental data. The system helps users analyze flood-related parameters and provides an estimated flood risk percentage through an interactive web dashboard.

This project was developed as part of the **AI-ML-and-GEN-AI Track** and demonstrates the application of machine learning techniques in disaster management.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Predict flood risk using Machine Learning.
- Analyze environmental and disaster-related parameters.
- Provide a user-friendly web interface.
- Assist in early flood risk assessment.
- Support disaster preparedness and decision-making.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Flood Prediction Dashboard
- Machine Learning Model Integration
- Interactive User Interface
- Flood Risk Percentage
- Data Visualization using Chart.js
- Responsive Web Design

